OL,3,CFirst Minister to urge Tata to 'look
OL,4,Cagain' at furnace plan on India visit
OL,6,FThe First Minister will visit India
OL,7,Fnext week to push for Tata Steel to
OL,8,F"look again" at its plans to shut
OL,9,Fblast furnaces which could cost
OL,10,Fthousands of jobs.
OL,12,FLast week, confirmed it is shutting
OL,13,Fits furnaces in after rejecting a last-
OL,14,Fminute union plea to change its plans.
OL,16,Fhas announced his intention to visit
OL,17,FMumbai to ask the company to
OL,18,Freconsider the future of steel
OL,19,Fproduction in Wales.
