OL,6,FWhile unions and politicians have
OL,7,Fcriticised the decision, Tata has said
OL,8,Fit is planning the biggest investment
OL,9,Fin the steel industry for decades,
OL,10,Fsafeguarding the industry and
OL,11,Fpreserving 5,000 jobs.
