OL,3,CFirst Minister to urge Tata to 'look
OL,4,Cagain' at furnace plan on India visit
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Senedd on Tuesday, Mr
OL,7,FGething said: "Next week, I plan to go
OL,8,Fto Mumbai to meet Tata to press the
OL,9,Fcase again not just for the
OL,10,Falternative, but a clear case that we
OL,11,Fhave continued to make and will
OL,12,Fcontinue to make for there to be no
OL,13,Fhard compulsory redundancies, and to
OL,14,Flook again at the opportunities for
OL,15,Fsteel within Wales and Britain, and
OL,16,Fwhat it will mean not just for our
OL,17,Frenewable future, but the general
OL,18,Ffuture of our economy."
