OL,3,CFirst Minister to urge Tata to 'look
OL,4,Cagain' at furnace plan on India visit
OL,6,FThe First Minister added that the
OL,7,Fcompany's plans could have an indirect
OL,8,Fimpact on more than 10,000 people.
OL,10,FJeremy Miles, the Cabinet Secretary
OL,11,Ffor Economy and Energy, also made a
OL,12,Fstatement to the Senedd in which he
OL,13,Fsaid it was "extremely disappointing"
OL,14,Fthat Tata had not taken up proposals
OL,15,Ffor a transition to lower carbon
OL,16,Fsteelmaking.
OL,18,FThe plan, developed by unions, would
OL,19,Fhave seen one blast furnace maintained
OL,20,Fthrough the transition.
