OL,6,FThe company has said this would have
OL,7,Fincurred at least #1.6 billion of
OL,8,Fadditional costs.
OL,10,FMr Miles said: "It is essential that
OL,11,Fthe company now does all it can to
OL,12,Favoid compulsory redundancies within
OL,13,Fits loyal workforce and works with the
OL,14,FTransition Board to ensure the
OL,15,Faffected employees receive the
OL,16,Fappropriate help and guidance to
OL,17,Freskill or seek employment."
