OL,3,CFirst Minister to urge Tata to 'look
OL,4,Cagain' at furnace plan on India visit
OL,6,FHe called on Tata to provide details
OL,7,Fand timing for the impact on its
OL,8,Fworkforce to ensure the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment could provide support,
OL,10,Fincluding skills and training to find
OL,11,Fnew employment.
OL,13,FMr Miles added: "We will also urge
OL,14,FTata to give their workers and supply
OL,15,Fchain, wherever feasible, the
OL,16,Fopportunity to work on the
OL,17,Fdecommissioning and construction phase
OL,18,Frequired to move to electric arc
OL,19,Fsteelmaking.
