OL,6,F"Preparatory work begins in December
OL,7,Fthis year and could therefore offer
OL,8,Fcontinuity of employment for some
OL,9,Fworkers."
OL,11,FTata Steel's chief executive and
OL,12,Fmanaging director T V Narendran said
OL,13,Flast week that the company's plans
OL,14,Fwere the "most viable proposal" and
OL,15,Fwould secure the long-term future of
OL,16,Fthe business, while preserving "the
OL,17,Fmajority of jobs in the UK".
